reviewText: Got the movies before due date. Love the movie concept.  Woman are the main heroes and like all angry partners they get payback . Lol
Product arrived with a minor mix up, but was corrected in record time, with an additional movie (which I also love).
crazy, crazy Japanese horror/comedy that does not disappoint!!!
American reprint has quality issues. I bought Lust of Dead 4 Japanese version and the visual quality was a lot better.
